<a class="carousel-item active">
<div class="fluid-iframe">
<img alt="" class="fluid-element" data-title="斯洛文尼亚球员在打破僵局后，跑到球迷面前疯狂庆祝，但最终还是无缘三分。（路透社）" src="https://dss1.zbstatic1.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2024/06/20/2024-06-20T143153Z116992607UP1EK6K14D3Y4RTRMADP3SOCCER-EURO-SVN-SRB-REPORT.JPG?2864827"/>
